snippet.title: Building the New Line UK Playthrough
snippet.description:
Special thanks to BoCoTheDiesel for helping me set up the UK version


welp here's another gameplay of a Thomas PC game this time it's the UK version of Building the new line sadly not really a full gameplay as i couldn't do everything that happens in the game and i skipped the first  track set you could build cause i felt like that wasn't needed but still enjoy!


something very special might be coming soon too~


Thomas and Friends is owned by Mattel Creations

The Game is owned by Stunt Puppy Entertainment, Inc./Infogrames
